_sText:
Mole-O-Rama, A collection of maps made by myself (m0le) for your enjoyment.

>awp_mohammed
A desert themed awp map, with an underwater passage and a pusher to get you across the water

>fy_swastika
8 Boxes, 1 Swastika, Hours of fun

>fy_swastika_2
16 boxes, 2 swastikas, not as good as the original but still fun-ish

>HypnoToad
Hypnotic, but not a toad, players are push along a rectangular track and must kill each other, but dont fall off!. Complete with fog!

>PMP4EVER
Pizza Mc Puff, the serious clan for serious people, co-founded by cunning linguist 2d0ngz, this is one of our official clan maps, complete with hidden teleporters, death pits, and traps which leave you stuck in the air!

>PRECISELY
Yet another ratatoing joke. The 2 teams must launch themselves over a wall to kill the opposition, Includes custom textures!

>RATATOING
The terror that started it all, Ratatoing includes twin, breakable, towers, ladders, water, and traditional Ak's vs. M4 gameplay.

>SkateSesh
An experimental map, players must slide along a track dealing with ramps, death lasers and thin bars, also includes a surf section, when you complete it, you start again with a shotgun! (m3)

>Slalom
A silly surf-style map, players 'ski' down a slope, which has loads of walls, these walls are pass-throughable but they deal about 90 damage to you if you pass through them. once at the bottom, pick up a deagle (or an AK or a M4) and battle to the death with any survivors!

(c) 2008 all these maps belong to me, m0le, if you wish to de-compile and edit them, make sure you have my permission first!
